{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tags-js","path":"/tags/react/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Aleks Popovic - personal website and blog"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"totalCount":5,"edges":[{"node":{"excerpt":"A couple of days ago I noticed something interesting in the Netflix mobile app. It has a Coming Soon page which shows movies and TV shows…","fields":{"slug":"/How-to-build-Netflix's-Coming-Soon-page-in-React/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"November 02, 2020","title":"How to build Netflix's Coming Soon page in React","series":null,"description":"A couple of days ago I noticed something interesting in the Netflix mobile app. It has a Coming Soon page which shows movies and TV shows that are soon coming to Netflix. It has a few interesting functionalities. It's loading data from somewhere and sorting it into cards. You can bookmark a movie to let Netflix know you want to be notified when it comes out. It has a cool, modern looking share menu for which you need to manage state.","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":3.1746031746031744,"src":"/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/bc8e0/netflix.png","srcSet":"/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/8ac63/netflix.png 200w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/3891b/netflix.png 400w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/bc8e0/netflix.png 800w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/6050d/netflix.png 1200w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/00405/netflix.png 1600w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/0e6e2/netflix.png 1920w","srcWebp":"/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/ccdb5/netflix.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/6b183/netflix.webp 200w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/fc32b/netflix.webp 400w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/ccdb5/netflix.webp 800w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2fdf/9000d/netflix.webp 1200w,\n/static/781e83aa64ca3df72c2c636e999b2